  "title": "呼籲參與：EMNLP 2024 BoF 研討會 - 探討 Embeddings、Reranker 與小型 LMs 在優化搜尋上的應用",
  "html": "<p>歡迎於 <strong>2024 年 11 月 14 日上午 10:30 至中午 12:00（邁阿密時間）</strong>參加在 EMNLP 2024 邁阿密會議上舉辦的 Birds of a Feather (BoF) 研討會，主題聚焦於 embeddings、rerankers 和用於優化搜尋的小型 LMs。繼<a href=\"https://jina.ai/news/a-tale-of-two-worlds-emnlp-2023-at-sentosa/?ref=jina-ai-gmbh.ghost.io#embeddings-roundtable-a-birds-of-a-feather-at-emnlp-2023\">2023 年在新加坡 EMNLP 成功舉辦 Embeddings BoF</a> 之後，本次為期 1.5 小時的實體會議將匯集專精於 embedding 模型、rerankers 以及資訊檢索相關領域的研究人員。會議將包含演講和專家討論環節，這是探討搜尋基礎模型最新進展、向專業觀眾分享您的研究成果，以及討論 2024 年搜尋模型新趨勢的絕佳機會。歡迎所有 EMNLP 現場與會者參加。</p><h2 id=\"event-details\">活動詳情</h2><ul><li>日期：2024 年 11 月 14 日（星期四）</li><li>時間：上午 10:30 - 中午 12:00（邁阿密時間）</li><li>地點：Miami Lecture Hall</li><li>形式：實體會議</li></ul><h3 id=\"calendar-links\">行事曆連結</h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=EMNLP+2024+BoF%3A+Embeddings%2C+Reranker%2C+Small+LMs+for+Better+Search&dates=20241114T103000%2F20241114T120000&ctz=America%2FNew_York&details=Join+us+for+a+Birds+of+a+Feather+%28BoF%29+session+at+EMNLP+2024.%0A%0ATopics+of+Interest%3A%0A-+Advanced+embedding+architectures%3A+multimodal%2C+multilingual%2C+cross-lingual%2C+and+cross-modal+approaches%0A-+Efficient+retrieval+paradigms%3A+late-interaction+models%2C+sparse-dense+hybrid+systems%0A-+Resource-efficient+approaches%3A+lightweight+architectures%2C+compression%2C+Matryoshka+Representation+Learning%0A-+Learning+methodologies%3A+instruction-tuning%2C+contrastive+learning%2C+zero%2Ffew-shot+adaptation%0A-+Evaluation+and+benchmarking%3A+MTEB+frameworks%2C+metrics+for+embeddings+and+RAG%0A-+System+optimization%3A+attention+mechanisms%2C+real-time+retrieval%0A-+Foundation+models+for+search%3A+LLM-based+embeddings%2C+small+LMs%0A%0ALocation%3A+Miami+Lecture+Hall%0A%0AFor+more+event+details%2C+please+visit%3A+https%3A%2F%2Fjina.ai&location=Miami+Lecture+Hall%2C+EMNLP+2024&ref=jina-ai-gmbh.ghost.io\">加入 Google 日曆</a></li><li>或下載 iCalendar/ics 檔案：</li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-file-card\"><a class=\"kg-file-card-container\" href=\"https://jina-ai-gmbh.ghost.io/content/files/2024/11/emnlp2024-bof.ics\" title=\"Download\" download=\"\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-contents\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-title\">emnlp2024-bof</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-caption\"></div><div class=\"kg-file-card-metadata\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-filename\">emnlp2024-bof.ics</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-filesize\">854 Bytes</div></div></div><div class=\"kg-file-card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><defs><style>.a{fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5px;}</style></defs><title>download-circle</title><polyline class=\"a\" points=\"8.25 14.25 12 18 15.75 14.25\"></polyline><line class=\"a\" x1=\"12\" y1=\"6.75\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"18\"></line><circle class=\"a\" cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11.25\"></circle></svg></div></a></div><h2 id=\"registration\">報名</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScXmwLyE1Xye-FuWblIHszERde1SmVEOAtxatZcKRB4lOEVrg/viewform?usp=sf_link&ref=jina-ai-gmbh.ghost.io\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">EMNLP 2024/BoF: Embeddings, Reranker, Small LMs for Better Search</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">What: A BoF (Birds of a Feather) in-person session on Embeddings, Reranker and Search LMs, co-organized by EMNLP PC and Jina AI. When &amp; Where: Date: Thursday, November 14, 2024\nTime: 10:30 AM - 12:00 PM (Miami Time)\nLocation: Miami Lecture Hall\nHighlights: multimodal embeddings, long context embeddings, multi- and bilingual embeddings, embeddings for low-resource languages, applications of embeddings, and the interplay between embeddings and prompts. Participation: The session is open to everyone; you can simply walk in to participate. If you're interested in contributing to this BoF, we welcome you to fill in the details below.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://jina-ai-gmbh.ghost.io/content/images/icon/android_192.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Google Docs</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://jina-ai-gmbh.ghost.io/content/images/thumbnail/5MYJcxbNpb8Z9Sw1zP7Lea67kBwmfp4XLQLFkFmBCZFma0k7NO966bupITjWHDHkC5yp_WQKJWg-w1200-h630-p\" alt=\"\" onerror=\"this.style.display = 'none'\"></div></a></figure><p>雖然一般參與無需事先報名，但我們強烈建議參與者透過 Google 表單進行報名，以協助我們更好地籌備本次會議。如果您希望在本次 BoF 會議中發表研究（10 分鐘時段）或擔任討論小組成員，請在報名表中註明。這是向 embeddings 和搜尋模型領域專家分享您研究成果的絕佳機會。</p><h2 id=\"topics-of-interest\">主題範疇</h2><ul><li>多模態、多語言、跨語言和跨模態的 embeddings 與 rerankers</li><li>Late-interaction 模型（如 ColBERT、ColPali）和 late chunking</li><li>長文本 embedding 模型</li><li>Embedding 和 reranker 模型的指令微調</li><li>基於 LLM 的 embedding 模型</li><li>用於文件閱讀的小型語言模型</li><li>高效且輕量級的 embedding 架構、注意力機制和優化</li><li>零樣本/少樣本檢索和適應方法</li><li>用於檢索的對比學習方法</li><li>Matryoshka Representation Learning、Embedding 壓縮和量化</li><li>混合稀疏-密集檢索系統</li><li>搜尋模型的領域適應</li><li>MTEB、Embedding、Reranker、RAG 評估指標和基準測試</li><li>用於程式碼和結構化資料的 embedding 模型</li><li>隱私保護 embedding 技術</li></ul>",
